comments: Gobert (UTA) establishes himself in a screening position with his arms extended slightly forward prior to marginal contact occurring with Rubio (MIN).
Okogie (MIN) brushes Conley's (UTA) right arm and marginal contact occurs as Conley drives toward the lane.
Okogie (MIN) extends his arm forward and slight contact occurs with Gobert's (UTA) lower half and left arm as Gobert attempts to control the pass, which he is able to do momentarily after.
Russell (MIN) is positioned sideways in a screening position and he does not extend into Mitchell's (UTA) path or otherwise deliver contact.
O'Neale (UTA) has an arm placed against Russell's (MIN) arm but the contact is marginal and he quickly removes it before Russell enters his shooting motion.
Rubio (MIN) and Conley (UTA) come together at the spot beyond the perimeter and marginal body contact occurs as Conley spins off.
Russell (MIN) extends into Conley's (UTA) path and initiates body contact with Conley that affects his SQBR.
Bogdanovic (UTA) brings his arms forward and marginal contact occurs with Okogie's (MIN) front as the hand-off takes place.
Okogie (MIN) brings his off-arm toward Bogdanovic's (UTA) front and marginal contact occurs as the hand-off takes place.
O'Neale (UTA) briefly places his right hand to Russell's (MIN) front as Russell starts driving toward the lane, and the contact is marginal.
Russell (MIN) brings his off-arm to O'Neale's (UTA) front and quickly releases as marginal contact occurs near the top of the key.
O'Neale (UTA) is in a vertical position at the time of the contact with Beasley (MIN).
Towns (MIN) and Gobert (UTA) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Conley (UTA) extends his left arm outward toward Russell (MIN) after the hand-off and marginal contact occurs as Russell contests the jump shot.
Russell (MIN) swings down and makes contact across Clarkson's (UTA) right arm during his upward shooting motion.
Gobert (UTA) and Towns (MIN) make incidental foot-to-foot contact with one another as Towns attempts to set the pick.
Towns (MIN) establishes himself in a screening position in Mitchell's (UTA) path and does not deliver the contact.
Russell (MIN) makes contact with Mitchell's (UTA) right arm that causes his hand to come off of the ball after his gather.
Conley (UTA) commits the take foul on Rubio (MIN).
Russell (MIN) and Ingles (UTA) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Ingles (UTA) commits the take foul on Russell (MIN).
Okogie (MIN) brushes Gobert's (UTA) backside/right shoulder during rebounding and marginal contact occurs prior to Gobert gaining control of the ball.
Bogdanovic (UTA) fails to inbound the ball within five seconds.
Culver (MIN) and Clarkson (UTA) come together at a spot during the inbound and incidental body contact occurs. Clarkson's reaction is not consistent with the amount of contact.
Russell (MIN) and Gobert (UTA) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Mitchell (UTA) commits the take foul on Russell (MIN).
